snippet.title: Super Boss Gaiden for Super Nintendo Playstation (Official trailer & download link)
snippet.description:
Download: http://superbossgaiden.superfamicom.org/
Please share your feedback for the game here, we will use it for an upcoming project! https://goo.gl/forms/wqNcFkTZtXyUMQw73

Update Feb 2018: V 1.2 was released! It fixes miscelangelous small bugs reported from players and includes a weird little challenge for a slightly altered ending: Try to carry the lobby piano through the game till the ending!

Update Dec 2017: V 1.1 was released, it fixes some small bugs, lessens slowdowns and has enhanced animations for player 2 & 3 - Enjoy! :)

Official trailer for the brand new Super Nintendo Playstation game Super Boss Gaiden! Are you ready for the full extend of the jam?!

Fully playable Super Nintendo Playstation version, also available as normal SNES ROM. 
Featuring awesome chiptune music by LHS https://soundcloud.com/lhschiptunes
